    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "in v4 we have this solved as `if (!this._isSearchStalled && !this._searchStalledTimer) {` is changed to `if (!this._isSearchStalled && !this._searchStalledTimer && this.helper.lastResults) {` and leaving the rest as-is. This will mean the render will no longer happen and can't cause errors",
